WEBVTT



00:00:00.864 --> 00:00:04.992
This sermon is brought to you by Buford Road Baptist Church.

00:00:04.768 --> 00:00:08.160
the speaker today is Pastor Tony Kahoot

00:00:08.672 --> 00:00:09.696
So,

00:00:10.496 --> 00:00:13.824
The idea was, after the choir went down,

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:17.728
That these lights would be dimmed and our ushers would come.

00:00:17.536 --> 00:00:19.616
And light these candles,

00:00:20.448 --> 00:00:23.360
And then they would start at the back, and they would.

00:00:23.616 --> 00:00:24.704
Let

00:00:24.704 --> 00:00:29.184
The folks out in the back, row by row, family by family, to come forward.

00:00:29.056 --> 00:00:31.872
And its replication was the.

00:00:32.032 --> 00:00:35.232
Passages in the Gospel of Matthew.

00:00:35.552 --> 00:00:38.368
In chapter two, when the wise men came.

00:00:39.968 --> 00:00:45.728
To the baby Jesus, the word says this in Matthew 2:11, and when they were coming to the house,

00:00:45.952 --> 00:00:50.784
They saw the young child with Mary, his mother, and fell down and worshipped him.

00:00:51.264 --> 00:00:53.984
And when they had opened their treasures,

00:00:54.304 --> 00:00:57.440
They presented unto him gifts.

00:00:57.824 --> 00:01:00.032
Gold and frankincense,

00:01:00.096 --> 00:01:01.280
And murm,

00:01:01.856 --> 00:01:11.904
And so our pastor in 1978 envisioned that as we would come forward, it would represent, as the wise men came to present Jesus, the baby child.

00:01:11.424 --> 00:01:12.416
child.

00:01:13.632 --> 00:01:15.136
Their gifts

00:01:15.168 --> 00:01:17.664
This was a way that we, as a church,

00:01:17.568 --> 00:01:19.296
Could present the Lord.

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.248
A very special love gift.

00:01:21.024 --> 00:01:24.544
Which is over and above our regular times and offerings, and so.

00:01:24.384 --> 00:01:27.168
It's been my pleasure, and pastor, too.

00:01:27.616 --> 00:01:31.200
Ape Simon did this and I have carried the solver.

00:01:31.456 --> 00:01:33.472
And has made it.

00:01:33.632 --> 00:01:36.544
A priority to keep pasture.

00:01:36.448 --> 00:01:38.464
Kay Wood's vision alive.

00:01:39.168 --> 00:01:42.048
you listen to Pastor Tony Kahoot

